That you're his adopted son?

632
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:14,080
When did you find out?

633
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:19,120
A little later than you.

634
00:32:37,520 --> 00:32:38,240
Why

635
00:32:39,320 --> 00:32:40,240
