651
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:38,000
has revealed your whereabouts.

652
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:39,720
I'm sorry.

653
00:33:39,720 --> 00:33:40,560
Brother Xie,

654
00:33:41,640 --> 00:33:42,720
