655
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:44,160
It's not your fault.

656
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:51,000
Brother Pei,

657
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:54,240
do you really think so?

658
00:34:04,520 --> 00:34:05,440
But

659
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:08,520
